captures/

# Vendored dependencies: the bridge server's node_modules are committed so the
# plugin installs with no `npm install` step. The repo-root .gitignore ignores
# every `node_modules` at any depth, so re-include this tree explicitly. The
# directory itself must be un-ignored before its contents, and the `**` rule
# also covers nested package node_modules (e.g. type-is/node_modules).
!server/node_modules
!server/node_modules/**
!server/package-lock.json
